                        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-100 uppercase tracking-tight">시큐어 코딩: 소유권 검증 로직 (Ownership Validation)</h3>
                    </div>
                    <div class="pl-14">
                        <p class="text-sm text-slate-400 mb-6 leading-relaxed">
                            데이터베이스 조회 시 반드시 현재 세션의 사용자 ID를 조건절(WHERE clause)에 포함시켜 권한을 강제합니다.
                        </p>
                        <div class="bg-slate-950 rounded-xl p-6 font-mono text-sm shadow-inner relative">
                            <div class="absolute top-4 right-4 text-green-600 text-[10px] uppercase font-black italic">backend_logic.py</div>
                            <div class="text-slate-200">
                                <span class="text-pink-500">def</span> <span class="text-cyan-400">get_user_profile</span>(request, profile_id):<br>
                                &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;current_user_id = request.user.id<br><br>
                                &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class="text-slate-500 italic"># BAD: profile = Profile.objects.get(id=profile_id)</span><br>
                                &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class="text-slate-500 italic"># GOOD: 요청된 ID와 현재 로그인한 사용자의 ID를 함께 검증</span><br>
                                &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;profile = Profile.objects.filter(id=profile_id, user_id=current_user_id).first()<br><br>
                                &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class="text-pink-500">if not</span> profile:<br>
                                &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class="text-pink-500">return</span> Response({"error": "Unauthorized Access"}, status=403)
